      "cooked": "<p>Në vijim te listes, do ishin keto filma :</p>\n<p><em>mertitojne te shihen:</em></p>\n<ol start=\"11\">\n<li>The woman who ran (Hong Sang-soo, Kore e Jugut)</li>\n<li>Cuban Network (Olivier Assayas, France)</li>\n<li>Days (Tsai Ming-Liang, Tajvan)</li>\n<li>Family Romance, LLC (Werner Herzog, Gjermani)</li>\n<li>Malmkrog (Cristi Puiu, Roumani)</li>\n<li>Peninsula (Yeon Sang-ho, Korea e Jugut)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>çka… :</em></p>\n<ol start=\"17\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2020/09/03/tafmaja-e-madhe-te-le-pa-gje-tenet-film-amerikan-me-regji-te-christopher-nolan/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Tenet</a></strong> (Christopher Nolan, USA)</li>\n<li>A girl missing (Koji Fukada, Japoni)</li>\n<li>Gjerat qe themi, gjerat qe bejme [Les Choses qu’on dit, les choses qu’on fait] (Emmanuel Mouret, France)</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2020/06/24/minikeizmi-i-dukshem-i-njeriut-te-padukshem-the-invisible-man-film-amerikan-me-regji-te-leigh-whannell/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Invisible man</a></strong> (Leigh Wannell, USA)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>Humbje kohe :</em></p>\n<ol start=\"21\">\n<li>Verë 1985 [Eté 85] (François Ozon, France)</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2020/08/26/light-of-my-life-film-amerikan-me-regji-te-casey-affleck/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Light of my life</a></strong> (Casey Affleck, USA)</li>\n<li>Dwelling in the Fuchun Mountains (Gu Xiaxogang, Kinë)</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2020/07/29/dark-waters-film-amerikan-me-regji-te-todd-haynes/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Dark waters</a></strong> (Todd Haynes, USA)</li>\n<li>Madre (Rodrigo Sorogoyen, Spanje)</li>\n</ol>",
