      "cooked": "<p>sipas NY Times :</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/03/movies/best-movies.html\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/d/a/da724c3f80e17332490b1085c432b1179878755d.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/03/movies/best-movies.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"10:00AM - 03 December 2020\">nytimes.com – 3 Dec 20</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/533;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/a/0a06bc28a9668604f3e842d5dee585c032ad4f7e_2_800x533.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/a/0a06bc28a9668604f3e842d5dee585c032ad4f7e_2_800x533.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/0/a/0a06bc28a9668604f3e842d5dee585c032ad4f7e.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/0/a/0a06bc28a9668604f3e842d5dee585c032ad4f7e.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/a/0a06bc28a9668604f3e842d5dee585c032ad4f7e_2_10x10.png\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/03/movies/best-movies.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Best Movies of 2020 (Published 2020)</a></h3>\n\n  <p>The screening rooms were closed. The festivals were virtual. The blockbusters were in storage. Even so, our critics found abundant and inspiring signs of cinematic life in the pandemic.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
