      "cooked": "<p>dhe THE NEW YORKER :</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.newyorker.com/culture/2020-in-review/the-best-movies-of-2020\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/f/afa2a452b2ddbca51d214b4c11035f1a1bdc2051.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/culture/2020-in-review/the-best-movies-of-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"11:00AM - 02 December 2020\">The New Yorker – 2 Dec 20</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/450;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f38f8163127ce6b7d8afee91529873a48c6c5579_2_800x450.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f38f8163127ce6b7d8afee91529873a48c6c5579_2_800x450.png, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f38f8163127ce6b7d8afee91529873a48c6c5579_2_1200x675.png 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/f/3/f38f8163127ce6b7d8afee91529873a48c6c5579.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f38f8163127ce6b7d8afee91529873a48c6c5579_2_10x10.png\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/culture/2020-in-review/the-best-movies-of-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">The Best Movies of 2020</a></h3>\n\n  <p>None of these thirty-six films has made a difference in the nation’s crises this year—but inner truth of experience and authenticity of emotion are, in and of themselves, cleansing to a defiled mediasphere.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
